According to the local news report  a fire outbreak has occurred at one of Sri Trang Gloves (Thailand) Public Company Limited ( STGT ) 's production plant on Sunday morning 21 Feb 2021  which the firefighters brought the fire under control after 30 minutes with no casualties or injuries reported.STGT stated that the impact from the fire is limited  but the commercial of date (COD) for this new plant will be delayed by another 1-2 months.
